trans-unit.source: Reset Virtual Network Gateway Shared Key
trans-unit.target: Reset Virtual Network Gateway Shared Key

trans-unit.source: The <embeddedLabel>Reset Virtual Network Gateway Shared Key</embeddedLabel> operation generates a new shared key with a specified character length.
trans-unit.target: The <embeddedLabel>Reset Virtual Network Gateway Shared Key</embeddedLabel> operation generates a new shared key with a specified character length.

trans-unit.target: Request

trans-unit.source: The <embeddedLabel>Reset Virtual Network Gateway Shared Key</embeddedLabel> request may be specified as follows.
trans-unit.target: The <embeddedLabel>Reset Virtual Network Gateway Shared Key</embeddedLabel> request may be specified as follows.

trans-unit.source: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;subscription-id%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the subscription ID, <codeInline>%%amp;lt;virtual-network-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the virtual network associated with the gateway, and <codeInline>%%amp;lt;local-network-site-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the local network site associated with the shared key.
trans-unit.target: Replace <codeInline>%%amp;lt;subscription-id%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the subscription ID, <codeInline>%%amp;lt;virtual-network-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the virtual network associated with the gateway, and <codeInline>%%amp;lt;local-network-site-name%%amp;gt;</codeInline> with the name of the local network site associated with the shared key.
